\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Liz's Christmas eve feast is ready to serve. The only thing missing is the mystery guest. After a few minutes of some wild guesses, the mystery guest knocks on the door and is revealed. It was Evan and Liz's mom! The rest of the evening was live with conversation around the dinner table, with Sarah slowly warming up to the idea that these strangers truly do consider her a new and welcome member of the family.<!$Scr_Ps::4>}
