\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 This was the final scene in the chapter, at least for the moment. In the previous scene, Sarah had met Liz, and after a moment of horror, thinking Liz was upset with her, all had been well, and Sarah had been warmly welcomed into Liz's apartment and her family.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Sarah stepped away to get changed, using that time to secretly sneak in some email and text replies, only to admonish herself for prioritizing a few last-minute work tasks over her time with Evan and his family. She had promised Evan that she would not work while they were visiting Liz, and after faltering on that promise, she came to dinner ready to embrace the experience of this visit \endash  free of work concerns. Well, at least she tried her best to be free of work concerns.<!$Scr_Ps::4>}
